item.title: Second_test
item.author: Quechen YANG
item.description: Just install latest version of  Hugo (> 0.62.0) for your OS (Windows, Linux, macOS). Why not support earlier versions of Hugo? Since Markdown Render Hooks was introduced in the Hugo Christmas Edition, this theme only supports Hugo versions above 0.62.0. Hugo extended version is recommended Since some features of this theme need to processes  SCSS to  CSS, it is recommended to use Hugo extended version for better experience.
